      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tavistock%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Tavistock operates under New Jersey’s Walsh Act, governed by a three‑member commission elected at‑large.",
